4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science and Machine Learning course designed for beginners with no prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks with three classes per week, ensuring intimate learning with a maximum class size of 12. Students will learn key skills including Python, SQL, and statistical analysis, and will engage in practical applications to solve real-world problems. The course prepares participants to create predictive models and implement AI projects through the development, deployment, and maintenance stages.

Certificates are awarded upon completion, recognized by multiple organizations. The course is available in both English and Spanish.

